GloriousCallingS讚tean美ofT之aiseP泉   GloriousCallingS zàn tean měi ofT zhī aiseP quán
EnglishTranslation:SOP,RachelYang〔羅12:1；提後2:20；林後9:8,4:7；腓3:14〕詞、曲：曾祥怡   EnglishTranslation SOP RachelYang luó tí hòu lín hòu féi cí qǔ céng xiáng yí
•=66全心敬拜地、呼喊地GraceTseng   quán xīn jìng bài dì hū hǎn dì GraceTseng
